description: Atvexa AB engages in the operation of a property company for schools, preschools, special care, and childcare. The company is headquartered in Stocksund, Stockholm and currently employs 2,592 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-12-13. The firm operates more than 10 subsidiaries, which own over 70 preschools, around 15 schools and a special school, located throughout Sweden. Preschools operate under such names as TP Forskolor, Waga & Wilja, Framtidsfolket, Unike, Skrattegi, M3P Forskolor, Mabra, Byangsskolan, Sodervikskolan, Akers Friskola, Ralsen, Montessori i Norrtalje, Engelska Skolan Norr, MA Vatterosen and Angdala Skolor. The Company’s main shareholders comprise Svenska Rehabiliterings Sjukhus AB and Alteria Holding AB.
name: Atvexa AB
